  <div class="section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      An end-to-end training request system that captures, routes, and tracks training
      needs across the plant. Supervisors and associates submit requests through a simple
      form; Power Automate handles routing, approvals, and notifications.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Key Capabilities</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Standardized intake form for all training requests</li>
      <li>Automated routing to the appropriate trainer or department</li>
      <li>Approval workflows integrated with Teams notifications</li>
      <li>Centralized request log for reporting and follow-up</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
